","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底要牛汁應該落單叫埋定嘢食到咗再叫?之前試過被人屌落單唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該落單個時叫埋，咁佢地可以一次過做晒"},{"pid":"e809f67ad298f13dbb7ddcffed54dc3c5f440ba6","tid":91994,"uid":15503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:19:51.000Z","msg":"見到樓主個名就諗起之前嗰單強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89c54defc08d9d044e8a49861980d4436cae9b3","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪得我一個覺得吉野家嘅牛肉飯根本唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n次次去親都食野菜煎雞飯/東坡肉飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得東坡仲難食喎，又肥，啲汁又難食"},{"pid":"3ef972b61a9ca7c4ac8892cc4e60b588fd617936","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係要飽食咩最抵</blockquote><br />\n唔知，做開廚房，唔知啲價錢"},{"pid":"e25cdd9248298e7536eea7943017a1874f37fced","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪員工任食牛肉，肥婆係咪會真係比多d牛比d客，邊個餐你最鐘意</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n唔會，有話大約係幾多，出餐個度會有個經理睇住，多得滯會叫你（不）返走<br />\n冇，食厭晒"},{"pid":"5b4f4ab1d2f111947719c5fed9174d4917058140","tid":91994,"uid":78494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:29:47.000Z","msg":"點睇而家啲火鍋？ 係咪好唔乾淨？"},{"pid":"d2b2da15b61f1da5916217be61a4387c6d6b9bdf","tid":91994,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>到底要牛汁應該落單叫埋定嘢食到咗再叫?之前試過被人屌落單唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該落單個時叫埋，咁佢地可以一次過做晒</blockquote><br />\n試過落單叫<br />\n攞餐果時無比我"},{"pid":"194b4cc952ccf5ba0a2d5ea67118d5251fefc6f8","tid":91994,"uid":59051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:31:35.000Z","msg":"你𣈴撚準未？"},{"pid":"c803e83a4769a96ae84dcd21c038e7c32b179ca5","tid":91994,"uid":35653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你𣈴撚準未？</blockquote><br />\n你條撚準備？"},{"pid":"8f59e3a2adf5edd44c8a61cb11c59051a8a2080b","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>到底要牛汁應該落單叫埋定嘢食到咗再叫?之前試過被人屌落單唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該落單個時叫埋，咁佢地可以一次過做晒</blockquote><br />\n試過落單叫<br />\n攞餐果時無比我</blockquote><br />\n漏一次半次都唔過份姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e1dc134f878137e397781e1fe42cca4fe0c97f","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇而家啲火鍋？ 係咪好唔乾淨？</blockquote><br />\n完全唔價個個價，乾淨黎講都ok，唔會話好差"},{"pid":"9ad986c9b2b72d5f727382bd0f8cee240291e45f","tid":91994,"uid":78494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點睇而家啲火鍋？ 係咪好唔乾淨？</blockquote><br />\n完全唔價個個價，乾淨黎講都ok，唔會話好差</blockquote><br />\n我記得岩岩出既時間五十幾蚊 有飯有烏冬，而家加錢先有仲要貴左好多"},{"pid":"04763e6705e76d722bfef411dfd205b53a0414cd","tid":91994,"uid":78494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你𣈴撚準未？</blockquote><br />\n你條撚準備？</blockquote>門鎖好未？"},{"pid":"cc85290b5e631f1fd09e609a4e6dc71f001d4875","tid":91994,"uid":19053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"搖撚準未"},{"pid":"48362babd541be0eccf67e353da651aec02209a0","tid":91994,"uid":31629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:46:14.000Z","msg":"D炸野炸好放左幾耐<br />\n食親都係熱但係完全軟晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30ea0bce92c2bb0fd489f8475ebe4a9922d477a","tid":91994,"uid":45918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點睇而家啲火鍋？ 係咪好唔乾淨？</blockquote><br />\n完全唔價個個價，乾淨黎講都ok，唔會話好差</blockquote><br />\n我記得岩岩出既時間五十幾蚊 有飯有烏冬，而家加錢先有仲要貴左好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而加都係五十幾姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423945b069c3f96dbab65c13143d7046ba1de27b","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D炸野炸好放左幾耐<br />\n食親都係熱但係完全軟晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常都係即叫即炸，最多炸多一份備用"},{"pid":"85b9925c93e925946249710cc41e4d952a6da3f4","tid":91994,"uid":73750,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"牛肉系咪隔夜？d牛汁有無換過？"},{"pid":"e297f58d195c304c0a450a8f90bad9069edb1258","tid":91994,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪得我一個覺得吉野家嘅牛肉飯根本唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n次次去親都食野菜煎雞飯/東坡肉飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger"},{"pid":"e666667a42456706422f3e9366ce62076107c403","tid":91994,"uid":72929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"溫泉蛋點整？係咪用普通蛋都得？"},{"pid":"112b46b19661a957a9525c699e8b96a58889ae3a","tid":91994,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溫泉蛋點整？係咪用普通蛋都得？</blockquote><br />\n港孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483858d0f2553b5f8e467350ba6f0575127fecf6","tid":91994,"uid":8596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"有冇整過白汁牛飯當員工餐食？"},{"pid":"8bde81961e602e749beba555fb24e25f