ont-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高清拍攝</span></span></blockquote><br />\n冇，我做個間啲女唔係好掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcd2978558799c2d7985f47077b562d87862c50","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞飯嗰啲係咪照燒汁,成日想要多啲汁但唔夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，直接叫雞汁，我地都係用水溝出黎，有咩成份我都係好清楚，冇留意包裝"},{"pid":"cd902f84159fea8460a10698702ccfff589f40b6","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞飯嗰啲係咪照燒汁,成日想要多啲汁但唔夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以問佢拎汁，唔洗錢架"},{"pid":"b217221100b09a76a2145beb06b93cd4581e583e","tid":91994,"uid":34836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"點解你哋啲邊爐次次都落咁少湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到次次都一定要自己加咗湯先開始打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517646d8297ca2f7e00e4c287939d5eccee0a907","tid":91994,"uid":19530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"打邊粒個湯底係點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236bbd9b9f53a56b7f8a664561aa095b9b85b069","tid":91994,"uid":4037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"點解黑蒜油雞飯出得個一陣就唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食左2次之後就無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716a6a0589728e6b88fa5633ee901c60c7c83218","tid":91994,"uid":60834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"制服係咪換曬黑色個款？<br />\n我記得未換之前係深藍色<br />\n<br />\n之前返過一排，都算比較大舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df785dcd811014245e278f848c21062cc417626","tid":91994,"uid":27109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:31:12.000Z","msg":"濃湯用邊隻汁開，有冇圖，想買支試下屋企打"},{"pid":"6387e83c3582f115d7b7a089b02de005d07721f5","tid":91994,"uid":3434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"次次都叫大豬鮮檸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481d3765cdc66fcb287f5e08e3731392712a36aa","tid":91994,"uid":9091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你𣈴撚準未？</blockquote><br />\n你條撚準備？</blockquote>門鎖好未？</blockquote><br />\n條撚好味"},{"pid":"20f06f856e8fe96df7641e0cb26ad7e6cb8b9cf5","tid":91994,"uid":3434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次都叫大豬鮮檸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係有時豬肉好深色，有時好淋、有時好硬"},{"pid":"cb9080c5410fa0f62b35d31fd13f0a0873341d75","tid":91994,"uid":12513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:42:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>關東煮 係咪來貨就整好晒 加熱就上?<br />\n個關東煮湯係用粉開?</blockquote><br />\n唔係，有幾種都要用湯煮下<br />\n用汁開</blockquote><br />\n其實份約有保密協議 <br />\n利申 某間鋪AM"},{"pid":"d945cbbe28a070e6f242a5bf4672cb9245b8ceb4","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你哋啲邊爐次次都落咁少湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到次次都一定要自己加咗湯先開始打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個（不）應該係岩岩好，應該係出火鍋個人驚淥親"},{"pid":"d86193dd0c95ea836f0cdbd628e6db09ac838106","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打邊粒個湯底係點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊粒？有濃，清，味噌，邊