密協議 <br />\n利申 某間鋪AM</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗巴打們唔會爆我出黎呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b06a9c7fbfe49c7faf960c6ec18a9ba5ebf6538","tid":91994,"uid":77559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:59:53.000Z","msg":"打邊爐啲料跌撚左係地下就咁執番放落去<br />\n啲菜過期唔會理 照用<br />\n利申：做過吉野家"},{"pid":"2e79cb85b436ffaaa7a0f7e6fc1cb4bba4cf6755","tid":91994,"uid":10773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"多唔多人叫雞飯走雞汁要牛汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4962e3c5a7043942ec10bba84e1e770dc82a3b4","tid":91994,"uid":46332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"細牛 普通牛 輕盈牛   巨丼 份量到底差幾遠<br />\n尤其是外賣"},{"pid":"b44ca7e05c41dc85ed3f7f6fe2e749a172e2ef64","tid":91994,"uid":72631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多唔多人叫雞飯走雞汁要牛汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真，可以咁叫?"},{"pid":"c591f2b88d954f02c3ec9e839de2a4c8f4d05a25","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打邊爐啲料跌撚左係地下就咁執番放落去<br />\n啲菜過期唔會理 照用<br />\n利申：做過吉野家</blockquote><br />\n我會洗返乾淨or掉囉，過期唔會用，就算冇都唔會用，會去借貨"},{"pid":"fa5863be1e60e5e89eb853513d7b1d8807c3e88f","tid":91994,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多唔多人叫雞飯走雞汁要牛汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真，可以咁叫?</blockquote><br />\n可以"},{"pid":"0ecbddae96f8723cd41fa0f6358d17e3a6aef70c","tid":91994,"uid":10773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"